Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有邂逅 就定然會有離別之日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有辦法的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 若沒有邂逅 就不會有珍貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 離別的眼淚有一半是感謝的眼淚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 讓人害羞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 今天為了領取送去做定期檢查的鳳尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和艾莉西亞前輩來到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做思科威爾的鳳尾舟工房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 每一艘鳳尾舟都是匠人們手工製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作一艘鳳尾舟大概要花三個月左右的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用年限約為20年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每隔幾年都必須為鳳尾舟進行一次全面保養
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這艘鳳尾舟雖然已經用了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻是我重要的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 定期檢查的結果出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為已經用了蠻長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它還很好用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…如果只是自己用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是說句實話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它已經殘舊到讓客人乘坐會顯得失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那保留下來作練習用呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣鳳尾舟就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用次數減少的話 會加快老舊的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不能讓客人乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但用作搬運的話還能用很久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在每天都會使用它的主人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直工作到使用年限為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對鳳尾舟來說也是件幸福的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:12.43,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 與鳳尾舟的分別…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 燈裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然分別會很寂寞 但也不能對客人失禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大叔說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠跟每天使用自己的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這艘鳳尾舟一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏 明天你帶上相機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟這艘鳳尾舟一起去值得紀念的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是明天應該幫艾莉西亞前輩工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是燈裏用的鳳尾舟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 是真的鳳尾舟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟先生 今天開始請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水無燈裏 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好哦 燈裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…有句話不知該怎麼說好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你劃的方向反了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要照好多照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相機好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便當好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣也很好～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 鳳尾舟先生再見之旅啟程～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…咦咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…對不起 對不起 對不起 對不起…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不過今天找我到底什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鳳尾舟先生再見之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實今天出來是為了跟這艘鳳尾舟作最後的紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它已經破損得不能再搭載乘客了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們決定換一艘新的鳳尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生是我用這艘鳳尾舟接待的第一位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就想請你參加這次行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們就走第一次接待曉先生時的路線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬢子 載我去開往浮島的纜車站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏 是客人嗎 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 記得今天好像有檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纜車只開到六點為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六點…還有十五分鐘？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能趕上嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…以我的技術沒辦法趕上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是只付半熟手的船錢哦 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我不是你的客人嗎 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只是半熟手 不也是領航員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始 請允許我使用遮擋客人視線的劃法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯嘛 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 這就是終點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你今天陪我走這一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛一臉認真啊 馬尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥斯拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 愛麗絲 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小後輩是這個行動下一程的參加者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走好你的第二次人生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見了 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是熱血沸騰的男人 氣候調節員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將眼淚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去跟兩位前輩初次見面的那個岬角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次只拍鳳尾舟們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是給它添了許多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉強它做了許多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 誰叫它是你的鳳尾舟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它肯定在想 唉 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像鳳尾舟們也在談話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道別會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能在說讓人害羞的台詞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也坐過很多次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你你你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就沒哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個啊…那個…紅茶的水汽跑到眼睛裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是鳳尾舟先生再見之旅其三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的路線是單手套晉級考試的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考試時有不告訴考生這裏就是考試地點的傳統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時侯我也是完全不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考試的時候還是第一次來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時還以為被水攻了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個讓人昏昏入睡的悠閑靜謐的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:15:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏被領航員們稱為「希望之丘」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望之丘…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裏可以把新威尼斯盡收眼底
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格 恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏今天開始就是單手套了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長 我們來照相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…您什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才就一直坐著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能開始劃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但我還是半熟手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您要到哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到前面的分岔路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 您為什麼會在我的鳳尾舟上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一定是緣分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緣分嗎 真是個美麗的詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能…再坐一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這樣 再劃一段好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個老爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個場景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我第一次劃鳳尾舟時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 今天真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我們去吃晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 明天就是跟鳳尾舟分別的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏姐姐 我已經坐不上那艘鳳尾舟了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想好好跟它說再見啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 雨夜後的黎明…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
