Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:36.80,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}輕拂面頰的 溫柔的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:45.91,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌聲中搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:55.55,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身體裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:06.40,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}閉上雙眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:00:00.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}是風的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:24.75,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}來 讓我們出發 向著閃亮的波濤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:33.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}臉上的笑容 從未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:44.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}快 傳達到彼方 把這份感動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:54.55,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}托付給清風 帶到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:59.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水之精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
